49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=e15fdcc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=51a5da75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=401ba700\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests"},{"pid":"d04e1f792eb2d46f4d6435e4911d271dd32a4f04","tid":1631551,"uid":169195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d44de03ff4dff53adaafed13e4ff6175f5960d1","tid":1631551,"uid":49016,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:24.000Z","msg":"其實一直都無人話割<br />\n只係話等人權法過左先大搞特搞"},{"pid":"aa34018ee100dae5b642351f2dbac28f56531268","tid":1631551,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"越亂 証明林鄭越有用去平亂<br />\n<br />\n越亂就想美國唔好企我們呢到 影響法案辣度<br />\n<br />\n我們拉長嚟玩 條臭西趁越亂 乘機出師有名推其他法<br />\n<br />\n冚家產 蒙面法之後 佢點到會贏<br />\n<br />\n1） 更亂 可推其他乜撚緊急法 96小時乜春之類法<br />\n<br />\n2） 平靜咗 証明條蒙面法係有用 回復少少秩序之類<br />\n<br />\n所以條臭西點都贏<br />\n<br />\n但我地冷靜下先 亂同平靜D的結果 邊個畫面達到制裁目標容易些？ 當然我假設大家想班狗賊同我們欖炒! 記得謝蛇移民case? 呢D先至係我哋要的清算目標！<br />\n<br />\n所以 忍一下先 唔好比條臭西帶到我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},{"pid":"92c2b329338ea3d816c33927521c677a7ee2bf19","tid":1631551,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7d6e2cf59300099bea5d5ccce94709e044cc0383","tid":1631551,"uid":297686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:50.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"74909d9d3aedd01d0dea60d15c6140c0ae371f8a","tid":1631551,"uid":297686,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa34018ee100dae5b642351f2dbac28f56531268","tid":1631551,"uid":287211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:43.000Z","msg":"越亂 証明林鄭越有用去平亂<br />\n<br />\n越亂就想美國唔好企我們呢到 影響法案辣度<br />\n<br />\n我們拉長嚟玩 條臭西趁越亂 乘機出師有名推其他法<br />\n<br />\n冚家產 蒙面法之後 佢點到會贏<br />\n<br />\n1） 更亂 可推其他乜撚緊急法 96小時乜春之類法<br />\n<br />\n2） 平靜咗 証明條蒙面法係有用 回復少少秩序之類<br />\n<br />\n所以條臭西點都贏<br />\n<br />\n但我地冷靜下先 亂同平靜D的結果 邊個畫面達到制裁目標容易些？ 當然我假設大家想班狗賊同我們欖炒! 記得謝蛇移民case? 呢D先至係我哋要的清算目標！<br />\n<br />\n所以 忍一下先 唔好比條臭西帶到我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:05:11.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"82426bd86a3f60f6874dd8ca4ec60d3168f232bd","tid":1631551,"uid":42487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:22.000Z","msg":"天琦真係抗爭教課書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6da717b6bf99ed20e1f2a5bff4dc8715ac5bd90","tid":1631551,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79f66e846242e2df8ee344d03b48e3d32ef8e9c2","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62dced9a2831b6228e6cea6271d8dc18f595b8b","tid":1631551,"uid":37413,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b994bd2e00f1c29232ba57c95a5d798d86d3369c","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:09:56.000Z","msg":"美國從來都冇話香港示威者暴力"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:22:01.000Z","msg":"林奠而家咪不斷激嬲我哋囉, 你冇發覺裝修永冇POPO阻止咩<br />\n美國而家話唔割唔等於以後唔割喎, 凡事冇絕對, 唔好咁老定好<br />\n最重要真係唔好太過份"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:29:23.000Z","msg":"POPO係黎唔切姐，不知幾想打柒示威者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:23:34.000Z","msg":"咪玩啦嚟唔切<br />\n蒙面法前夕嗰晚喺元朗嗰度離狗屋車程只係兩分鐘，要嚟好快㗎咋<br />\n但手足玩咗成兩個鐘都冇人嚟啦<br />\n仲要好多區都冇阻止，佢要就係呢啲暴力破壞畫面<br />\n反正商店對佢哋冇損失，咪由你哋打囉，關我屁事"},{"pid":"9b55b81581a254eaa9907de7c9d92eb3dc17b777","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e3247d97d01cf899cfe79b3fb8777a2ecf7463b0","tid":1631551,"uid":206411,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:42:05.000Z","msg":"唔割<br />\n但係手足要有底線"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:24:57.000Z","msg":"只能夠講要有大原則<br />\nTK難免"},{"pid":"1613f275f1ff7f6cca4f48fdd638e1b19a87edfa","tid":1631551,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:25:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對店舖:記住唔需要次次硬裝修</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">1.打電話、EMAIL、無限FAX</span></span></strong><br />\n想同職員談心又得，講咩都得，幫阿SIR叫下外賣又得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />總知JAM到佢線就得。有EMAIL既就SEND EMAIL查詢下，有FAX機既可以用下無限FAX大法<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">2.MEMO紙</span></span></strong><br />\n有開門就入去叫杯水慢慢坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無開門既咪留張紙起度寫低自己有咩問或者有咩訴求囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">3.善用1823</span></span></strong><br />\n食完野集體食物中毒呀，消防設備唔合符規格呢D無理由唔投訴呀？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留意返打完1823之後，佢係要起限期內比返回覆你架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢招長玩長有，大家打之前要謹慎少少呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">4.蟲系魔法師</span></span></strong><br />\n知道好多巴絲打鐘意養蟲蟲，但係入店一定要小心唔好倒瀉D寶貝呀(特別起食肆)<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">對人(限影大頭相/沒有攻擊性/非主攻類):</span></strong></span><br />\n記住召喚神獸唔係唔得，必須記住係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: pink;\">對家首先用武力/拎住武器先可以召喚</span></strong></span><br />\n但係對住非攻擊形對手都召喚既話觀感就唔係太好睇，仲比左機會對家有煲大<br />\n對住非攻擊形既我地可以幫佢<strong><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">飛個靚髮</span></span></strong>或者<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\">化下妝</span></span></strong>就夠，唔一定要下下爆哂缸先叫成功架<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">*要記住中年人著緊自己把頭髮仲多過條命</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n呢場抗爭要贏一定要學識剛柔並用<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/ejjnAS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/ejjnAS</a>"},{"pid":"3cf98b97502e2a68a47c480a4a4e421404a79679","tid":1631551,"uid":235374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家太過focus係蒙面法 裝修 私了 忽略左緊急法帶來既經濟危機 大家要明白呢一點 呢個係港共最大春袋</span></span>"},{"pid":"f914369362ba81693fe13d9ce146744589771459","tid":1631551,"uid":40543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:14.000Z","msg":"唔割！！但大家做嘢要諗一諗，唔好比情緒支配咗！"},{"pid":"763611e8fdf915bb02cf3b67e2133a2fe3b05249","tid":1631551,"uid":302475,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>一個準則可以破到而家死局</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1632239/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"d9c8ca3f648e46970ac0d19ae056f23671208574","tid":1631551,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:35.000Z","msg":"林鄭都幾狗，拎商界同市民做子彈"},{"pid":"d3df2135124e4fa90c103f7eb4df9d4cc92b6553","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8db669047cf447bcb8ab3b0975b72d45d569d3a","tid":1631551,"uid":69646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0178c6efb66c06d3f0d81879db9cb3e8bca7cd08","tid":1631551,"uid":158404,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:54:28.000Z","msg":"唔割 要理性處理"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:27:43.000Z","msg":"前線根本係根據現場環境決定行動<br />\n例如：有手足要幫拖，義氣仔女頂硬上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n冇辦法好似冷氣軍師有咁多資訊<br />\n例如：原來裝修錯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca585a126b502c4e55c0f6ebbdb8c96f5177a94e","tid":1631551,"uid":7484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:28:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"965c156b99a107c8a90340a9cc41ea46210315b6","tid":1631551,"uid":221265,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0a20c86106decbd4874b7778465c8a215cef8d7","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T15:47:25.000Z","msg":"佢等左好耐，香港人仍然未割蓆<br />\n佢相信香港人係有底線<br />\n佢相信升級到某個位<br />\n一定有人割蓆<br />\n<br />\n最近終於升級到：<br />\n有手足裝修錯鋪<br />\n有手足獅鳥錯人<br />\n有手足軍營附近詠香江<br />\n<br />\n佢今日等到，你會割嗎？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/pk_RYcfN_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fpk_RYcfN_1200x0.png&h=58496dd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://www.mingpaocanada.com/van/ftp/News/20160217/HK/_17ga301.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mingpaocanada.com%2Fvan%2Fftp%2FNews%2F20160217%2FHK%2F_17ga301.jpg&h=dda91688&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://news.memehk.com/img/post/14250_654651.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.memehk.com%2Fimg%2Fpost%2F14250_654651.jpg&h=8dc8fec9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BSKXWvW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBSKXWvW.png&h=38aa260b&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:20.000Z","msg":"Yes<br />\n<br />\n所以佢周六先會任破壞<br />\nPopo唔出動/hea出動"},{"pid":"3214fbbb8c4a4e99a601fba371d5016317c48897","tid":1631551,"uid":133235,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:29:45.000Z","msg":"小心高級五毛話你極端勇武分化撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"186ac8dd614de535b0