a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=e15fdcc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fworld-asia-china-49949548&h=20132a5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/news/world-asia-china-49949548</a><br />\nAnti-government marches in Hong Kong have ended in rioting, with attacks on government offices, a metro station and businesses with ties to mainland China.<br />\n<br />\nCNN:<br />\n<a href=\"https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=51a5da75\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2019%2F10%2F05%2Fasia%2Fhong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk%2Findex.html&h=53844d7e\" target=\"_blank\">https://edition.cnn.com/2019/10/05/asia/hong-kong-protests-mask-emergency-intl-hnk/index.html</a><br />\nViolent protests which began Friday stretched into the early hours of Saturday, beyond the midnight deadline when the new anti-mask regulations began. They spread out across the city and soon devolved into violent clashes, with protesters throwing petrol bombs and police responding with pepper spray and tear gas.<br />\n<br />\nUN rights chief :<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hongkongfp.com%2F2019%2F10%2F06%2Fun-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence&d=lN%2BDZ8lYvPdYiEl1IYcsL4gmK84TLJm0fByd7TIP4s4%3D&h=401ba700\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hongkongfp.com/2019/10/06/un-rights-chief-troubled-alarmed-hong-kong-violence</a><br />\nUN human rights chief Michelle Bachelet said Saturday she was &ldquo;troubled&rdquo; by Hong Kong&rsquo;s increasingly violent pro-democracy protests"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:30:38.000Z","msg":"頭兩個係事實描述，唔關事<br />\n依家係有violence，冇人會唔認同，但原因係暴政引起<br />\n<br />\n第三個係佢覺得暴力示威咁到煩惱，但冇譴責過任何野<br />\n<br />\n唔該學下英文先，唔好見到violence就出黎帶風向<br />\nok？"},{"pid":"b8dac4cdcefd69138232ab88b1fad9c4bce962e6","tid":1631551,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:10.000Z","msg":"其實無人話要割 只係想件事做得更精準 可以做到抗爭無沙石"},{"pid":"3ce22668bbbdabdf519929add9845cf6b4503d46","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8b045968b2e959b3e5199c018a03deed385a2536","tid":1631551,"uid":39092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:21.000Z","msg":"同意<br />\n打死都唔割 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:25.000Z","msg":"割蓆只會通向運動失敗，係唔會通向成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ba1ce20f728fb7a07776d0150050f62c926745d","tid":1631551,"uid":178453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"核爆都唔割<br />\n爭取民主<br />\n兄弟爬山  各自努力"},{"pid":"f6b9422fba9e3aafe08f3734c9f7f2423817591f","tid":1631551,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:33:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68ed25b86d2836d66eb1dd035070df59248a76bb","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c6da717b6bf99ed20e1f2a5bff4dc8715ac5bd90","tid":1631551,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"79f66e846242e2df8ee344d03b48e3d32ef8e9c2","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a62dced9a2831b6228e