我哋！<br />\n<br />\n我不是叫大家晤搞 只是拉長嚟玩 有先後次序<br />\n<br />\n我哋翻新黨鐵計劃延遲二三星期 黨鐡仲會係到 所以押後一下！ 大家想想！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:37:29.000Z","msg":"第一句已經唔認同，唔通唔亂就代表林鄭冇用？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718306551ccca9696ee3605c3617b20b4a5221f7","tid":1631551,"uid":73915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92c2b329338ea3d816c33927521c677a7ee2bf19","tid":1631551,"uid":322775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:03:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:01.000Z","msg":"升級係唔會影響人權法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4a3b9947d2a82d9765686af0e795954df6bf2ed","tid":1631551,"uid":259319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:38:38.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">[18區開花] 一句講晒，聽日一點定八點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631933\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631933</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span>"}]}